    "content.chapter.06-operation.header_ref": "CH.06 — OPERATION",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.1.text": "工作前准备",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.item.1": "務必將產品放置在平整稳固的平麵，且產品背部和右侧散熱孔處不能放置任何东西，以免阻擋散熱。產品与墙或物品之間距離必須 ≥ 120 mm（4.7 in），以確保通風良好。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.2.item.2": "若第一次使用產品，或距離上一次很長時間没有使用產品，請先運行一次清潔程序。請參閱 CH.08 維護保養中的清潔說明。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.3.text": "產品開機",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.4.item.1": "给產品接通電源，產品發出“滴”一聲，所有按鍵點亮後再熄灭，表示已經接通電源。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.4.item.2": "然後點擊 **Power** 按鍵，按鍵显示白燈，產品已處於開機狀態。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.5.text": "如何製作子弹冰",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.6.step.fill_tank.text": "给子弹冰水箱中注滿水，注水至水位刻度處。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.6.step.open_lid.text": "打開腔蓋，並取出子弹冰篮和水箱。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.block.6.step.seat_tank.text": "然後將水箱放入子弹冰內腔，請用手按壓下水箱，確保已經裝到位。水箱鬆動可能導致產品無法工作。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page1.section_title": "操作指引",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.1.step.return_basket.text": "然後放入子弹冰篮，並關閉腔蓋。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.1.step.select_size.text": "點擊 **Make Ice** 按鍵，切換點亮按鍵上方的 S / M / L 指示燈，選擇需要製作的子弹冰尺寸。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.1.step.start_cycle.text": "選擇完尺寸後，產品自動開始製作子弹冰。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.2.item.1.label_before": "ICE FULL →",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.2.item.2.label_before": "ADD WATER →",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.item.1": "製冰中途可點擊 **Make Ice** 按鍵切換製冰尺寸。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.item.2": "製冰中途可點擊 **Power** 按鍵終止，子弹冰製冰按鍵燈熄灭，產品停止子弹冰製冰。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.item.3": "當產品檢测到子弹冰冰篮裝滿後，**ICE FULL** 警示燈點亮為绿燈，產品停止製冰。待冰融解，或取走後，產品会自動恢復製冰。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.item.4": "請留意，製冰期間若 **ADD WATER** 警示燈點亮红燈，產品会停止製冰，請及時给水箱补充水。",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.block.3.title": "提示 NOTICE",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.page.page2.section_title": "操作指引（續）",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.title": "操作指引",
    "content.chapter.06-operation.toc_title": "操作指引",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.header_ref": "CH.07 — TROUBLESHOOTING",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.header.1": "故障现象",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.header.2": "可能原因",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.header.3": "解決方案",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.1.cell.1": "不能開機",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.1.cell.2": "電源未連接或插座無電",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.1.cell.3": "檢查電源連接及插座是否正常。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.2.cell.1": "不能排水",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.2.cell.2": "排水膠塞未鬆開或排水口堵塞",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.2.cell.3": "檢查產品底部排水膠塞是否已鬆開；檢查排水口是否堵塞。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.3.cell.1": "不能製冰",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.3.cell.2": "水箱缺水（ADD WATER亮红燈）",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.3.cell.3": "给水箱加水至水位線。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.4.cell.1": "不能製冰",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.4.cell.2": "製冰模具只結霜無法結冰（管道無法抽水）",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.4.cell.3": "加水至水位線，静置半小時後重新啟動。观察製冰兜是否有注水，有則表示抽水泵已復位。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.5.cell.1": "製冰中途停止",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.5.cell.2": "冰篮已滿（ICE FULL亮绿燈）",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.5.cell.3": "取走冰块或等待冰融解，產品会自動恢復製冰。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.6.cell.1": "製冰中途停止",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.6.cell.2": "水箱缺水（ADD WATER亮红燈）",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.6.cell.3": "及時给水箱补充水，產品会自動恢復製冰。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.7.cell.1": "前5次冰块偏小",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.7.cell.2": "水溫较高，處於降溫阶段",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.7.cell.3": "属正常现象，冰形会随水溫下降逐渐增大，達到標准尺寸。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.8.cell.1": "製冰效果不理想",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.8.cell.2": "通風間距不足或環境溫度過高",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.8.cell.3": "確保四周≥120mm間距；將產品移至阴涼通風處。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.9.cell.1": "冰块不透明",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.9.cell.2": "水質矿物質含量高或水溫/環溫影響",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.1.row.9.cell.3": "使用TDS<200mg/L的纯净水；連續製冰偶尔不透明属正常现象。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.2.text": "如果用戶不按照本手册操作產品，並對產品造成任何損壞或質量問題，工廠、經銷商及品牌商將不承担任何责任。",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.block.2.title": "免责聲明 DISCLAIMER",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.page.page1.section_title": "故障排除",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.title": "故障排除",
    "content.chapter.07-troubleshooting.toc_title": "故障排除",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.header_ref": "CH.08 — MAINTENANCE",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.1.text": "自動清潔（製冰模具和製冰兜）",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.2.step.step1.text": "给水箱加水至水位線。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.2.step.step2.text": "開機狀態下，點擊 **Clean** 按鍵，按鍵燈亮白燈，產品自動清潔製冰兜和製冰模。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.2.step.step3.text": "清潔完成後，產品自動停止，按鍵燈熄灭。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.3.text": "排水操作",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.4.step.step1.text": "斷開電源，將產品放置到水槽旁。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.4.step.step2.text": "將產品底部的排水孔塞鬆脫，讓內腔的水排乾。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.4.step.step3.text": "排水完成後，將排水孔塞回原位。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.6.text": "日常保養",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.7.item.1": "定期用乾净的水清洗產品內部，建議**每天使用前清洗一次**。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.7.item.2": "用柔軟濕布擦拭產品外壳，請勿使用腐蚀性清潔劑。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.7.item.3": "請遵循自動清潔步驟清洗製冰模具和製冰兜。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.block.7.item.4": "清潔保養前請拔掉電源，待產品冷却後再進行處理。",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.page.page1.section_title": "維護保養",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.title": "維護保養",
    "content.chapter.08-maintenance.toc_title": "維護保養",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.header_ref": "CH.09 — INSTALLATION / STORAGE / DISPOSAL",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.1.text": "包裝運輸",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.2.item.1": "運輸過程中請保持平衡，防止倾翻；產品倾斜角不得大於 45°。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.2.item.2": "移動或運輸產品時應保持直立狀態，避免損壞壓缩機和製冷繫统。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.2.item.3": "運輸後需静置 4 小時，待冷媒稳定後再通電。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.3.text": "安裝",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.4.item.1": "請將產品安裝在平整、稳固、乾燥的臺麵上，不得倾斜放置。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.4.item.2": "搬運時不要推拉產品，以避免倾覆或損壞部件。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.4.item.3": "產品四周与墙或物品之間需保持至少 120mm（4.7\"）的間距，以確保通風和可維護性。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.4.item.4": "請远離熱源、蒸汽和阳光直射環境。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.5.text": "存儲与拆除",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.6.item.1": "長期存放前，請排空水箱和內腔中的水，並完成清潔与擦乾。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.6.item.2": "請將產品置於乾燥、通風環境中保存，避免重壓和潮濕。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.6.item.3": "本產品含電子元件和 R600a 製冷劑，不得与生活垃圾一同丟棄。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.6.item.4": "拆除或報废時，請聯繫授權回收機構或零售商，按當地法規進行環保處置。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.7.text": "請勿損壞製冷劑回路。若需要報废處理，請交由具备資質的废棄物處理機構回收，以避免對環境和人身安全造成風險。",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.block.7.title": "WEEE / R600a",
    "content.chapter.09-installation-storage-disposal.page.page1.section_title": "安裝運輸、存儲与拆除",
